  "chapter": {
    "number": 15,
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "content": [
          "The Song of Moses and the Lamb"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 1,
        "content": [
          "Then I saw another great and marvelous sign in heaven: seven angels with the seven final plagues, with which the wrath of God is completed."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 2,
        "content": [
          "And I saw something like a sea of glass mixed with fire, beside which stood those who had conquered the beast and its image and the number of its name. They were holding harps from God,"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 3,
        "content": [
          "and they sang the song of God’s servant Moses and of the Lamb:",
          {
            "lineBreak": true
          },
          {
            "text": "“Great and wonderful are Your works,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "O Lord God Almighty!",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "Just and true are Your ways,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "O King of the nations!",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "noteId": 4612
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 4,
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Who will not fear You, O Lord,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "and glorify Your name?",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "For You alone are holy.",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "text": "All nations will come and worship before You,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "for Your righteous acts have been revealed.”",
            "poem": 2
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "content": [
          "Preparation for Judgment"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 5,
        "content": [
          "After this I looked, and the temple—the tabernacle of the Testimony—was opened in heaven."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 6,
        "content": [
          "And out of the temple came the seven angels with the seven plagues, dressed in clean and bright linen and girded with golden sashes around their chests."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 7,
        "content": [
          "Then one of the four living creatures gave the seven angels seven golden bowls full of the wrath of God, who lives forever and ever."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 8,
        "content": [
          "And the temple was filled with smoke from the glory of God and from His power; and no one could enter the temple until the seven plagues of the seven angels were completed."
        ]
      }
    ],
